OL,3,CMore Welsh-speaking adopters could
OL,4,Chelp reach 1 million speakers target
OL,6,FThe National Adoption Service for
OL,7,FWales says more Welsh-speaking
OL,8,Fadopters could help meet the Cymraeg
OL,9,F2050 target.
OL,11,FIn 2017 the Welsh Government set a
OL,12,Fstrategic target for the number of
OL,13,FWelsh speakers to reach 1 million by
OL,14,F2050.
OL,16,FBut in the last census the number fell
OL,17,Fto 538,300 - just 17.8% of Wales.
