OL,3,CMore Welsh-speaking adopters could
OL,4,Chelp reach 1 million speakers target
OL,6,FAt the National Eisteddfod in
OL,7,FPontypridd, there are calls for more
OL,8,FWelsh Speakers to adopt, so that the
OL,9,F300 children waiting for adoption in
OL,10,FWales can learn Welsh.
OL,12,FGuto, who adopted with his partner,
OL,13,Fsays it was important for them as a
OL,14,FWelsh language
OL,16,Fhousehold, to teach their child Welsh,
OL,17,F"it was important for us that we were
OL,18,Fable to raise our child bilingually.
