OL,3,CMore Welsh-speaking adopters could
OL,4,Chelp reach 1 million speakers target
OL,6,F"We wanted to adopt a slightly younger
OL,7,Fchild, as we didn't want a child to
OL,8,Fhave already started school and then
OL,9,Fbe thrown into that household without
OL,10,Fknowing Welsh.
OL,12,F"When we were matched with our child,
OL,13,Fwe were able to meet with their birth
OL,14,Fparents - which was quite emotional,
OL,15,Fbut we learnt a lot.
OL,17,F"They told us things like the music
OL,18,Fthey would listen to while they were
OL,19,Fin birth mums' belly. It's something
OL,20,FI'd highly recommend, if it's
OL,21,Fpossible."
