OL,6,F"There is no such thing as children
OL,7,Fwith special needs being more work,
OL,8,Fit's different work. There was a huge
OL,9,Famount of support when we were
OL,10,Fadopting. The school and social
OL,11,Fworkers were amazing.
OL,13,F"There is a big stigma with people
OL,14,Fworrying about special needs but they
OL,15,Fare no different toother children.
OL,16,FChildren are all unique."
